# Terraform — local state files contain secrets in plaintext, use remote backend in prod
**/.terraform
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
**/*.tfplan
# Belt-and-suspenders explicit entries
terraform/terraform.tfstate
terraform/terraform.tfstate.backup
terraform/terraform.tfvars

# Secrets
.config

# Talos generated configs (contain secrets in plain text)
talos/*/clusterconfig/

# Helm charts cached locally by `kustomize build --enable-helm`
argocd/**/charts/

